PrecisAmendments to the BRITISH COLUMBIA SPORT FISHING REGULATIONS which adjust the quotas for certain species, update or add to the schedules of waters where angling close times, fishing gear or other restrictions and prohibitions apply, and make other minor revisions that update and clarify the wording of the Regulations.

precis:
Amendments to the BRITISH COLUMBIA SPORT FISHING REGULATIONS which adjust
the quotas for certain species, update or add to the schedules of waters
where angling close times, fishing gear or other restrictions and
prohibitions apply, and make other minor revisions that update and clarify
the wording of the Regulations.
